title: 08 - How to Stop Toxic Thoughts {IF 2020}
description:
Anxious? Lonely? Depressed? You're not alone. God has given us a way out of our spiraling toxic thoughts and has given you the power to change. We hope this moment from IF:Gathering 2020 encourages and challenges you today!

Read Jennie's book 'Get Out of Your Head': https://www.amazon.com/Get-Out-Your-Head-Stopping/dp/1601429649

Watch IF:Gathering 2021 from ANYWHERE on March 5-6th, 2021. Sign up here: IFGATHERING2021.COM

Thanks HelloFresh! Go to HelloFresh.com/MADEFORTHIS10 and use code MADEFORTHIS10 for 10 free meals, including free shipping.
